            <text>Work done obtained is maximum in:</text>
            <option id="A">Reversible process</option><option id="B">Irreversible process</option><option id="C">Adiabatic</option><option id="D">Isochoric</option>
            <answer>A</answer><explanation>Theorem.</explanation>
        </question>
        <question>
            <text>Slope of Adiabatic curve is ___ than Isothermal:</text>
