            <answer>A</answer><explanation>T1=373, T2=273. eta = 1 - 273/373 = 100/373 ~ 26.8%.</explanation>
        </question>
        <question>
            <text>P-V diagram is a circle. Work done is:</text>
            <option id="A">Area pi R1 R2 (units)</option><option id="B">Zero</option><option id="C">2pi R</option><option id="D">Undefined</option>
            <answer>A</answer><explanation>Careful with units of P and V axes.</explanation>
        </question>
        <question>
            <text>Cyclic process clockwise in PV diagram. Work is:</text>
            <option id="A">Positive</option><option id="B">Negative</option><option id="C">Zero</option><option id="D">Undefined</option>
            <answer>A</answer><explanation>Expansion is upper curve.</explanation>
